<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Eb    Bb   Gm           F
 Nima desam Rabbim menga hayot sovgʻa qilding,
.Eb     Bb     Gm        F
 Tushuntirolmasman menga aziz ekanliging.
.Eb       Bb      Gm          F
 Meni Sen qutqarding, hayotim Sening qoʻlingda,
.Eb      Bb      Gm         F
 Va har kuni Rabbim, Sening nuring porlar menda.

[V2]
 Har kuni Rabbim, haqiqatda men yurarman,
 Iltijo qilib Seni bilishni xohlayman.
 Tanlagin (Yetaklagin) Rabbim, qadamlarimni boshqarib,
 Va har kuni Rabbim, Sening nuring porlar menda.

[C1]
.     Eb   Bb       Gm   F
   // Har kuni Sen bilan yashayman.
.  Eb   Bb    Gm   F
   Har kuni Senga ergashaman.
.  Eb   Bb       Gm       F
   Har kuni Sen bilan yashayman. //
.      Bb(Gm)           F
   /// Sen bilan doim yashayman. ///
.        Eb Bb Gm
   Sen bilan!__</lyrics>
<title>Nima Desam Rabbim ҲСХМ111</title>
